dct_title_s: Federal Street to Pine Street along the Cooper River
dct_description_sm: Map covers area of Cooper River from Federal Street to Pine Street. Map shows property lines, high water lines, face of concrete wharf lines, and exterior wharf lines. There is a letter attached to the map from Henry Sherman the assistant engineer to Victor Gelineau the director and secretary of the State of New Jersey Board of Commerce and Navigation.
